    "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nCompiling code below with `cython --shared=_cython reproducer.pyx` will result with following stacktrace:\n\n```python\nFile \"/home/dev/cython/.venv/bin/cython\", line 10, in <module>\n    sys.exit(setuptools_main())\n             ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Main.py\", line 822, in setuptools_main\n    return main(command_line = 1)\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Main.py\", line 850, in main\n    result = compile(sources, options)\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Main.py\", line 741, in compile\n    return compile_multiple(source, options, cache)\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Main.py\", line 700, in compile_multiple\n    result = compile_single(source, options, full_module_name=options.module_name, cache=cache, context=context)\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Main.py\", line 671, in compile_single\n    return run_pipeline(source, options, full_module_name, context)\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Main.py\", line 567, in run_pipeline\n    err, enddata = Pipeline.run_pipeline(pipeline, source)\n                   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Pipeline.py\", line 418, in run_pipeline\n    data = run(phase, data)\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Pipeline.py\", line 400, in run\n    return phase(data)\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Pipeline.py\", line 50, in generate_pyx_code_stage\n    module_node.process_implementation(options, result)\n    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/ModuleNode.py\", line 315, in process_implementation\n    self.generate_c_code(env, options, result)\n    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/ModuleNode.py\", line 647, in generate_c_code\n    self.generate_declarations_for_modules(env, modules, globalstate)\n    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/ModuleNode.py\", line 863, in generate_declarations_for_modules\n    vtab_list, vtabslot_list = self.sort_type_hierarchy(modules, env)\n                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/ModuleNode.py\", line 798, in sort_type_hierarchy\n    assert key not in vtabslot_dict, key\n           ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\nAssertionError: __pyx_array_obj\n```\n\n### Code to reproduce the behaviour:\n\n```cython\ncdef void memoryview_func_a(double [:] x):\n    x[0] = 1\n\ndef test_memview_wrapping():\n    cdef a = memoryview_func_a\n```\n\n\n### Expected behaviour\n\n_No response_\n\n### OS\n\nLinux\n\n### Python version\n\n3.14\n\n### Cython version\n\nmaster\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
